  ?humanGene skos:prefLabel ?humanGeneName . # Get human gene name

              up:disease ?disease .

    BIND("CC(C1CCC2C1(C(CC3C2CCC4C3(CCC(C4)C)C)C)C)C" AS ?cholestane_smiles)

    ?sachem_query sachem:query ?cholestane_smiles ;
